  "text": "Remark 1. Recently, Killip-Vişan [CITATION_1] have combined the ideas of the proof of Threorem 2, as applied to NLS in [CITATION_2] , with another important new idea, to extend Theorem 1 to the non-radial case for N ≥ 5.",
